The paper deals with image analysis using convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of multi-task learning is also a key aspect of the paper, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves medical imaging, which could be categorized under computer science and medicine (cs.MS) or multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the use of coordinate constraints and conditional adversarial modules suggests a focus on generative models, which could fall under artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
